																		Author Notes
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203746" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;" >Zyn</a></span> <span class="odate time_1429682660 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">22 Apr 2015 06:04</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2275403">
									

<p>Okay, wow. This took a long, long time to write. I think it was conceptualized a few months ago, only started getting written up two months ago, and has gone through 9001.5 revisions (interspersed by me playing Pokemon games until inspiration whacked me over the head again) up until now.</p>
<p>Many, many thanks to these awesome people:</p>
<ul>
<li>Clef for an insane amount of trimming help and brainstorming scenes and dialogue and also direct edits seriously Clef thank you so much</li>
<li>thedeadlymoose for helping with plotline, characterization, and technique (scorpion scene!)</li>
<li>DrMann for character cameo and phrasing help he is good with the words yes</li>
<li>Riemann for being tough on the pacing and plot development</li>
<li>Decibelles for scrutinizing the word choice</li>
<li>Eskobar for pointing out inconsistencies in character portrayal</li>
<li>Dexanote for discussing overall feel of the piece</li>
<li>Kain for commenting on inherent characterization and buildup</li>
<li>MacLeod, Gaffsey, username_null, tahunu, FoggyGolem, lurkd, NRuien, Petrograd, and MisterFlames for reading it in chat</li>
<li>And of course, if I forgot anyone, my apologies. You’re all the best.</li>
</ul>

							</div>

								
					
