<p>&#8230;huh. I actually didn't see it that way.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I&nbsp;dunno&nbsp;if&nbsp;these&nbsp;are&nbsp;spoilers,&nbsp;but&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;safe&nbsp;side...</a></div>
