<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">yeah&nbsp;okay&nbsp;they're&nbsp;probably&nbsp;definitely&nbsp;spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>There <em>are</em> at least a few traits that in-character Zyn Kiryu and IRL Zyn share, but I didn't write the tale to mirror the SCP writing process. I do write a lot of &quot;day in the life&quot;/slice of life stories for the wiki though, so this is sort of an extension of that, plus setting up a character for Resurrection.</p>
<p>Also, Zyn Kiryu doesn't actually create SCP-2332, but rather, a preliminary prototype of it. What she actually does with the light butterfly will be revealed later. ;)</p>
